text: Coedydd a Chorsydd Aber Teifi (Teifi Estuary Woodlands & Marshes) is a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion, west Wales. ==See also== *List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion Category:Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion
